name: I do not know you but I know we are Friends

metadata.name: Second Friend - Swiped and signed
metadata.description:
1/1 Swiped and signed edition.

I do not know you, but I know we are Friends is a collection of 1/1 silk printed mixed media work. The artworks are influenced by popular culture, media and art, and how we as humans live with bots all around us, swiping through life in search of purpose and meaning.

Collector of the NFT may request the physical work by contacting the artist directly, studio@aliphant.io. Physical work is 50x50cm.

This is an ongoing collection, and there will be more artworks that will contain elements from these pieces.
